item.title: The Power of Pressing Pause
item.description: When you're dealing with a stressful situation, your first instinct might be to act immediately to solve it. Unfortunately, acting immediately often means you don't think your actions through. Acting rashly can worsen the situation, making it even more stressful. Fortunately, there's a better way to respond to stress. All you have to do is take a few seconds to press the pause button... Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/you-are-not-a-frog/
